@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xvxsic(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(tmp + 0.55) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.24)))
    tmp = 0.24
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.60) + tmp) + v1)
    v1 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.52 - v0 + 0.86) + tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
